<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --navy: #0D1B40;
    --navy2: #162354;
    --blue: #1565C0;
    --green: #2ECC71;
    --green2: #27AE60;
    --amber: #F39C12;
    --red: #E74C3C;
    --white: #FFFFFF;
    --lgray: #F5F7FA;
    --mgray: #8A9BB0;
    --dgray: #2D3E55;
    --border: #E0E6EF;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
  body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif; color: var(--dgray); background: #fff; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* HERO */
  .hero { background: var(--navy); padding: 50px 20px 50px; text-align: center; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .hero::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: -80px; right: -80px; width: 400px; height: 400px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(46,204,113,0.06); }
  .hero::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: -60px; left: -60px; width: 300px; height: 300px; border-radius: 50%; background: rgba(46,204,113,0.05); }
  .hero-inner { max-width: 780px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; z-index: 1; }

  .hero-badge { display: inline-block; background: var(--green2); color: #fff; font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 6px 16px; border-radius: 20px; margin-bottom: 22px; }

  .hero h1 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(26px, 5vw, 44px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 18px; }
  .hero h1 em { color: var(--green); font-style: normal; }
  .hero-sub { color: var(--mgray); font-size: clamp(15px, 2.5vw, 18px); max-width: 580px; margin: 0 auto 28px; line-height: 1.7; }

  /* PRICE */
  .hero-price { margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .price-main { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(52px, 9vw, 78px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; }
  .price-main em { color: var(--green); font-style: normal; }
  .price-note { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 4px; }

  /* CTA BUTTON */
  .btn-cta { display: inline-block; background: var(--green); color: var(--navy); font-size: clamp(16px, 2.5vw, 20px); font-weight: 900; padding: 20px 52px; border-radius: 50px; text-decoration: none; letter-spacing: 0.3px; transition: transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.15s; box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(46,204,113,0.45); cursor: pointer; border: none; animation: ctaPulse 2s ease-in-out infinite; }
  .btn-cta:hover { transform: translateY(-3px); box-shadow: 0 14px 44px rgba(46,204,113,0.6); animation: none; }
  .btn-cta:active { transform: translateY(0); }
  @keyframes ctaPulse { 0%, 100% { box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(46,204,113,0.45); } 50% { box-shadow: 0 8px 44px rgba(46,204,113,0.75); } }

  .hero-guarantee { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 14px; }
  .hero-guarantee strong { color: #fff; }

  /* SECTIONS */
  section { padding: 64px 20px; }
  .container { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .section-tag { display: inline-block; color: var(--green2); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: 1.5px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  h2 { font-size: clamp(22px, 4vw, 34px); color: var(--navy); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1.2; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  h2 em { color: var(--green2); font-style: normal; }
  .section-sub { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 40px; max-width: 560px; }

  /* STATS BAR */
  .stats-bar { background: var(--green); padding: 40px 20px; }
  .stats-grid { max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(160px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; text-align: center; }
  .stat-num { font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 48px); font-weight: 900; color: var(--navy); line-height: 1; }
  .stat-label { font-size: 13px; color: var(--navy2); font-weight: 600; margin-top: 6px; }

  /* PAIN */
  .pain-section { background: var(--lgray); }
  .pain-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 16px; margin-top: 32px; }
  .pain-card { background: #fff; border-radius: 12px; padding: 22px; border-left: 4px solid var(--red); }
  .pain-icon { font-size: 24px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .pain-card h3 { color: var(--navy); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .pain-card p { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }

  /* COST SECTION */
  .cost-section { background: #fff; }
  .cost-box { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0D1B40 0%, #162354 100%); border-radius: 20px; padding: 40px; max-width: 700px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; }
  .cost-box h3 { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(20px, 3.5vw, 28px); font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .cost-row { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 14px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  .cost-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .cost-label { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8); font-size: 15px; text-align: left; }
  .cost-val { font-weight: 900; font-size: 16px; color: var(--red); white-space: nowrap; margin-left: 16px; }
  .cost-val.good { color: var(--green); }
  .cost-total { margin-top: 24px; padding-top: 20px; border-top: 2px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.3); }
  .cost-total p { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .cost-total strong { color: var(--green); font-size: 24px; font-weight: 900; }

  /* KIT */
  .kit-section { background: var(--navy); }
  .kit-section h2 { color: #fff; }
  .kit-section .section-tag { color: var(--green); }
  .kit-section .section-sub { color: var(--mgray); }
  .kit-items { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .kit-item { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.2); border-radius: 14px; padding: 28px 24px; transition: border-color 0.2s, background 0.2s; }
  .kit-item:hover { border-color: rgba(46,204,113,0.5); background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  .kit-item-icon { font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .kit-item h3 { color: var(--green); font-size: 16px; font-weight: 800; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .kit-item p { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.6; }
  .kit-item ul { margin-top: 10px; padding-left: 0; list-style: none; }
  .kit-item ul li { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 12px; padding: 3px 0 3px 16px; position: relative; }
  .kit-item ul li::before { content: '✓'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; }

  /* WHATSAPP EXAMPLE */
  .whatsapp-wrap { text-align: center; }
  .whatsapp-header { background: #075e54; color: #fff; padding: 10px 16px; border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; max-width: 420px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .wapp-avatar { width: 32px; height: 32px; background: #25d366; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 16px; }
  .wapp-name { font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; }
  .wapp-status { font-size: 11px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); }
  .whatsapp-bubble { background: #dcf8c6; border-radius: 12px 12px 4px 12px; padding: 16px 20px; max-width: 420px; position: relative; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); margin: 0 auto; }
  .whatsapp-bubble::after { content: ''; position: absolute; bottom: 0; right: -8px; border: 8px solid transparent; border-left: 8px solid #dcf8c6; border-bottom: 0; }
  .whatsapp-bubble p { color: #111; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .whatsapp-bubble .wapp-time { color: #999; font-size: 11px; text-align: right; margin-top: 6px; }

  /* COMPARE */
  .compare-table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin-top: 32px; border-radius: 12px; overflow: hidden; }
  .compare-table th { padding: 14px 20px; font-size: 13px; font-weight: 800; text-align: center; }
  .compare-table th:first-child { text-align: left; }
  .compare-table th:nth-child(2) { background: var(--lgray); color: var(--mgray); }
  .compare-table th:nth-child(3) { background: var(--green); color: var(--navy); }
  .compare-table td { padding: 12px 20px; font-size: 14px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); text-align: center; }
  .compare-table td:first-child { text-align: left; color: var(--dgray); font-weight: 500; }
  .compare-table td:nth-child(2) { color: var(--mgray); }
  .compare-table td:nth-child(3) { color: var(--green2); font-weight: 700; }
  .compare-table tr:last-child td { border-bottom: none; }
  .compare-table tr:hover td { background: var(--lgray); }

  /* STEPS */
  .steps-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr)); gap: 24px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .step-card { text-align: center; padding: 28px 20px; background: var(--lgray); border-radius: 14px; }
  .step-num { width: 44px; height: 44px; background: var(--navy); color: var(--green); font-size: 18px; font-weight: 900; border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  .step-card h3 { color: var(--navy); font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .step-card p { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 13px; }

  /* TESTIMONIALS */
  .testimonials-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr)); gap: 20px; margin-top: 36px; }
  .testimonial-card { background: var(--lgray); border-radius: 14px; padding: 24px; position: relative; }
  .testimonial-card::before { content: '"'; position: absolute; top: 12px; left: 18px; font-size: 48px; color: var(--green); font-family: Georgia, serif; line-height: 1; opacity: 0.4; }
  .testimonial-stars { color: #F39C12; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .testimonial-text { color: var(--dgray); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 14px; font-style: italic; }
  .testimonial-author { font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); font-size: 13px; }
  .testimonial-role { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 12px; }

  /* PRICE BOX */
  .price-section { background: var(--navy); text-align: center; }
  .price-section h2 { color: #fff; }
  .price-section .section-sub { color: var(--mgray); margin: 0 auto 40px; }
  .price-box { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 2px solid rgba(46,204,113,0.5); border-radius: 20px; padding: 44px 40px; max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .price-box-main { color: #fff; font-size: clamp(58px, 11vw, 80px); font-weight: 900; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .price-box-main em { color: var(--green); font-style: normal; }
  .price-box-note { color: var(--mgray); font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 28px; }
  .price-box-includes { text-align: left; margin-bottom: 32px; }
  .price-box-includes li { list-style: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 14px; padding: 7px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06); }
  .price-box-includes li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .price-box-includes li .ci { color: var(--green); font-weight: 700; font-size: 16px; }

  /* GUARANTEE */
  .guarantee-section { text-align: center; background: #fff; }
  .guarantee-badge { width: 110px; height: 110px; background: var(--green); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; font-size: 50px; margin: 0 auto 20px; box-shadow: 0 8px 40px rgba(46,204,113,0.4); }
  .guarantee-section h2 { max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto 16px; }
  .guarantee-section p { max-width: 520px; margin: 0 auto 24px; color: var(--mgray); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; }
  .guarantee-badge-text { display: inline-block; background: rgba(46,204,113,0.1); border: 2px solid var(--green); border-radius: 12px; padding: 12px 28px; color: var(--green2); font-weight: 800; font-size: 15px; }

  /* FAQ */
  .faq-section { background: var(--lgray); }
  .faq-list { margin-top: 32px; }
  .faq-item { background: #fff; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .faq-q { padding: 18px 20px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--navy); font-size: 15px; cursor: pointer; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center; user-select: none; }
  .faq-q::after { content: '+'; font-size: 20px; color: var(--green2); transition: transform 0.2s; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-q::after { content: '−'; }
  .faq-a { display: none; padding: 0 20px 18px; color: var(--mgray); font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.7; }
  .faq-item.open .faq-a { display: block; }

  /* FINAL CTA */
  .final-cta { background: var(--navy); text-align: center; padding: 80px 20px; position: relative; overflow: hidden; }
  .final-cta::before { content: ''; position: absolute; top: 50%; left: 50%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); width: 600px; height: 600px; border-radius: 50%; background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(46,204,113,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); }
  .final-cta h2 { color: #fff; max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto 12px; position: relative; }
  .final-cta p { color: var(--mgray); max-width: 460px; margin: 0 auto 32px; position: relative; }
  .final-cta .btn-cta { position: relative; }
  .final-cta-price { color: var(--green); font-size: 28px; font-weight: 900; margin-bottom: 6px; position: relative; }

  /* STICKY CTA */
  .sticky-cta { display: none; position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: var(--navy); border-top: 3px solid var(--green); padding: 12px 20px; z-index: 99; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 12px; }
  .sticky-cta-price { color: #fff; }
  .sticky-cta-price span { display: block; font-size: 11px; color: var(--mgray); }
  .sticky-cta-price strong { font-size: 22px; font-weight: 900; color: var(--green); }
  .sticky-cta .btn-cta { font-size: 14px; padding: 12px 28px; white-space: nowrap; animation: none; }

  /* FOOTER */
  footer { background: #080f24; color: var(--mgray); text-align: center; padding: 28px 20px; font-size: 13px; }
  footer a { color: var(--mgray); text-decoration: none; }
  footer a:hover { color: var(--green); }

  @keyframes popIn { from { transform: scale(0.85); opacity: 0; } to { transform: scale(1); opacity: 1; } }
  #exit-popup { display: none; }
  #exit-popup.active { display: flex !important; }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .sticky-cta { display: flex; }
    .hero { padding-bottom: 80px; }
    .final-cta { padding-bottom: 100px; }
    .price-box { padding: 32px 24px; }
    .cost-box { padding: 28px 20px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-inner">
    <div class="hero-badge">Material Prático para Clínicas Odontológicas</div>
    <h1>Sua clínica perde pacientes toda semana<br><em>por falta de processo na recepção.</em></h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">Scripts de WhatsApp prontos, checklist de rotina e planilha de faltas — tudo o que sua recepção precisa para funcionar com padrão, sem criar nada do zero. <strong style="color:#fff;">Acesso imediato.</strong></p>

    <div class="hero-price">
      <div class="price-main">R$<em>9,97</em></div>
      <div class="price-note">Pagamento único · Acesso imediato · Sem mensalidade</div>
    </div>

    <a href="https://pay.hotmart.com/M105446275H" class="btn-cta" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="margin-top:22px;display:inline-block;">
      Garantir meu Kit por R$9,97 →
    </a>
    <div class="hero-guarantee">🔒 <strong>7 dias de garantia total</strong> · Não gostou? Devolvemos tudo, sem perguntas</div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<div class="stats-bar">
  <div class="stats-grid">
    <div><div class="stat-num">10</div><div class="stat-label">Scripts de WhatsApp prontos</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">3</div><div class="stat-label">Checklists de rotina completos</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">Scripts de atendimento por telefone</div></div>
    <div><div class="stat-num">1</div><div class="stat-label">Planilha Excel com cálculo automático</div></div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- DOR -->
<section class="pain-section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-tag">O problema que você conhece bem</div>
    <h2>Quanto tempo sua recepção perde <em>criando coisas do zero</em>?</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">Toda clínica tem os mesmos problemas de recepção. Todos têm solução.</p>
    <div class="pain-grid">
      <div class="pain-card"><div class="pain-icon">📱</div><h3>Mensagem de confirmação toda hora</h3><p>A recepcionista digita o mesmo texto toda vez — diferente, incompleto e sem padrão.</p></div>
      <div class="pain-card"><div class="pain-icon">📋</div><h3>Abertura e fechamento no improviso</h3><p>Cada funcionária faz diferente. Quando alguém falta, a rotina vai por água abaixo.</p></div>
      <div class="pain-card"><div class="pain-icon">❌</div><h3>Pacientes que faltam sem avisar</h3><p>Sem controle de faltas, você não sabe quem é o problema — nem como resolver.</p></div>
      <div class="pain-card"><div class="pain-icon">📞</div><h3>Atendimento por telefone sem script</h3><p>Cada ligação é uma surpresa. Informações importantes ficam de fora ou são ditas de forma errada.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- QUANTO CUSTA NÃO TER -->
<section class="cost-section">
  <div class="container" style="text-align:center;">
    <div class="section-tag">A conta que ninguém faz</div>
    <h2>Quanto custa <em>não ter</em> o kit?</h2>
